            "content": [
              {
                "nodeType": "text",
                "value": "Thin as a reed from scant meals or a picky palate, this character lacks the brawn to heft a plow or haul water. They shiver through winters, too weak to keep up with sturdier folk. A hearty stew might help, but they\u2019d rather nibble than feast. Strength eludes their hollow frame.",
